&gt;&gt; &lt;a  rel="nofollow" href="https://github.com/mozilla/standards-positions/issues/1302"&gt;https://github.com/mozilla/standards-positions/issues/1302&lt;/a&gt;)
&gt;&gt;
&gt;&gt; *WebKit*: No signal (
&gt;&gt; &lt;a  rel="nofollow" href="https://github.com/WebKit/standards-positions/issues/558"&gt;https://github.com/WebKit/standards-positions/issues/558&lt;/a&gt;)
&gt;&gt;
