&gt; Finch feature name
&gt;
&gt; WebAppScopeExtensions
&gt; Rollout plan
&gt;
&gt; Will ship enabled for all users
&gt; Requires code in //chrome?
&gt;
&gt; False
&gt; Tracking bug
&gt;
&gt; &lt;a  rel="nofollow" href="https://bugs.chromium.org/p/chromium/issues/detail?id=1250011"&gt;https://bugs.chromium.org/p/chromium/issues/detail?id=1250011&lt;/a&gt;
&gt; Availability expectation
&gt;
&gt; Feature is available only in Chromium browsers for the foreseeable future.
&gt; No signal from other vendors.
&gt; Adoption expectation
&gt;
&gt; Feature is used by specific partner(s) to provide functionality within 12
&gt; months of launch in Chrome.
