&gt;&gt; Intent to Prototype:
&gt;&gt; &lt;a  rel="nofollow" href="https://groups.google.com/a/chromium.org/d/msgid/blink-dev/68aeedee.050a0220.27f047.019b.GAE%40google.com"&gt;https://groups.google.com/a/chromium.org/d/msgid/blink-dev/68aeedee.050a0220.27f047.019b.GAE%40google.com&lt;/a&gt;
