&lt;a  rel="nofollow" href="https://chromestatus.com/feature/5162372125818880"&gt;https://chromestatus.com/feature/5162372125818880&lt;/a&gt; has been updated to link
to the spec, and a standards position for Mozilla was filed:
&lt;a  rel="nofollow" href="https://drafts.csswg.org/css-color/#predefined-display-p3-linear"&gt;https://drafts.csswg.org/css-color/#predefined-display-p3-linear&lt;/a&gt;
